<#include "/common/base.ftl">
<@content>
    <div class="centre-wide">
        <div class="centre-wide generic-container">
            <h1>Welcome to AceOfGrades!</h1>
            <h5><i>"The best offline flashcard flipper to hit the internet"</i></h5>
            <p>Ever needed to do some flashcards but you forgot them?</p>
            <p>Ever wanted to do some online flashcards, but had no internet?</p>
            <p>Tell everyone about <u>aceofgrad.es</u>!</p>
            <p><i>Sponsored by the legendmixer foundation</i></p>
        </div>
        <div class="generic-container">
            <h2>AceOfGrades Development Noticeboard</h2>
            <div style="width: 100%">
                <hr style="color: white">
                <h3>Change Log - 26/4/26</h3>
                <p>Hello acers! Quick update for you all.</p>
                <ul style="list-style-position: inside">
                    <li>
                        Fixed an "internal server error" that would sometimes occur when clicking the profile page.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Improved card animation smoothness.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Increased card font size greatly on mobile and slightly on PC.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Removed home button on mobile to create more room.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        AceOfGrades logo changed to AOG on mobile to create more room.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        AceOfGrades logo / AOG logo now acts as a home button.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Added name and description of pack in pack page.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Added functionality of follow button. Followed cards appear in your "packs" page.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>- legendmixer</p>
            </div>
            <hr style="color: white">
        </div>
    </div>
</@content>